return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.3','translation-revision-date'=>'2025-08-03 08:10:44+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Plugins - SQLite Database Integration - Stable (latest release)','language'=>'zh_TW','messages'=>['The Query Monitor plugin will continue to function correctly after the change. You can safely proceed with the installation.'=>'進行變更後，Query Monitor 外掛仍會正確執行，因此網站管理員可以放心繼續安裝。','To enable SQLite support, this file will need to be replaced.'=>'如需啟用 SQLite 支援，必須替換這個檔案。','We’ve detected an existing database drop-in file at %s, created by the Query Monitor plugin.'=>'系統已偵測到由 Query Monitor 外掛建立、位於 %s 的資料庫強化外掛檔案。','WordPress database error:'=>'WordPress 資料庫錯誤:','The password you chose during installation.'=>'安裝時所設定的密碼。','User already exists. Password inherited.'=>'這個使用者已存在，將會沿用現有密碼。','Your chosen password.'=>'安裝過程中所設定的密碼。','<strong><em>Note that password</em></strong> carefully! It is a <em>random</em> password that was generated just for you.'=>'請小心<strong>記下密碼</strong>！這是個人專屬的<strong>隨機</strong>密碼。','Database size'=>'資料庫大小','Database file'=>'資料庫檔案','SQLite version'=>'SQLite 版本','Database type'=>'資料庫類型','Undefined'=>'未定義','Database: MySQL'=>'資料庫: MySQL','Database: MariaDB'=>'資料庫: MariaDB','Database: SQLite'=>'資料庫: SQLite','Install SQLite database'=>'安裝 SQLite 資料庫','By clicking the button below, you will be redirected to the WordPress installation screen to setup your new database'=>'網站管理員點擊下方按鈕後，便會重新導向至 WordPress 安裝畫面以設定新資料庫。','This plugin will switch to a separate database and install WordPress in it. You will need to reconfigure your site, and start with a fresh site. Disabling the plugin you will get back to your previous MySQL database, with all your previous data intact.'=>'啟用這個外掛會切換至獨立資料庫並將 WordPress 安裝於其中。網站管理員需要重新組態這個網站，並從全新網站開始。停用這個外掛之後，這個網站會切換回之前的 MySQL 資料庫，原有的資料均會保持不變。','Important note'=>'重要注意事項','All checks completed successfully, your site can use an SQLite database. You can proceed with the installation.'